                  <note type="family_structure">Includes parents in commemoration</note>
                  <note type="liturgical_context">Lazarus Sunday - pre-Easter resurrection theme</note>
                  <note type="perpetual_provision">Eternal foundation with curse protection</note>
                  <note type="ritual_details">Specific candle provision for requiem service</note>
